ies: `limma` and `data.table`.\\n2. Read the input files `input/normalized.csv` and `input/annotation.csv` using `fread` from the `data.table` package.\\n3. Convert the gene expression data to a matrix format suitable for `removeBatchEffect`.\\n4. Create a design matrix using the `group` column from the annotation data.\\n5. Use `limma::removeBatchEffect` to adjust the gene expression data for batch effects.\\n6. Write the corrected data to `output/integrated_data.csv` using `fwrite`, ensuring row names are preserved.\\n7. Verify the output file exists and submit the task as complete.\\n\\n**Note:** Ensure that the data matrix is numeric and does not contain any non-numeric values or row names that might interfere with the `removeBatchEffect` function.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}], "hide_old_env_states": false, "hide_old_action_content": false}, "next_agent_state": {"tools": [{"type": "function", "info": {"name": "run_shell", "description": "Run a shell command in the task work_dir (bash -lc).", "parameters": {"type": "object", "properties": {"command": {"description": "Shell command string passed to `bash -lc`.", "title": "Command", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["command"]}}}, {"type": "function", "info": {"name": "read_text_file", "description": "Read a UTF-8 text file relative to work_dir.", "parameters": {"type": "object", "properties": {"relative_path": {"description": "Path under the workspace (not absolute).", "title": "Relative Path", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["relative_path"]}}}, {"type": "function", "info": {"name": "write_text_file", "description": "Write text to a path under work_dir (creates parent dirs).", "parameters": {"type": "object", "properties": {"relative_path": {"description": "Path under the workspace (not absolute).", "title": "Relative Path", "type": "string"}, "content": {"description": "Full file body to write as UTF-8 text.", "title": "Content", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["relative_path", "content"]}}}, {"type": "functi